{"word":"H7599 - שָׁאַן - shâʼan - shaw-an' - Be at ease","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">שָׁאַן</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>shâʼan"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>shaw-an'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Be at ease"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - அமைந்திரு, அமைதியாயிரு, சுகிந்திரு, சுகமாய் வாழ்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"(Pilel) to be at ease, to be at peace, to rest, to rest securely, to be quiet"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> A primitive root; to <i>loll</i>, that is, <i>be peaceful</i>: - be at ease, be quiet, rest. See also <a href=\"#/H1052 - בֵּית שְׁאָן - Bêyth Shᵉʼân - bayth she-awn'/1052\">H1052</a>."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H7599 - שָׁאַן - shâʼan - shaw-an'/7599\">H7599</a>, <a href=\"#/H7600 - שַׁאֲנָן - shaʼănân - shah-an-awn'/7600\">H7600</a>"}]}